   <group id="18B0">
    <text id="Name">
     <orig>Canadian Aboriginal syllabics extended</orig>
     <transl>统一加拿大原住民音节文字扩展（Unified Canadian Aboriginal Syllabics Extended）</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="Text">
     <orig>Letters for Cree, Ojibwe ''(Algonquin)'', Carrier, Dene ''(Atabascan)''.</orig>
     <transl>用于克里语、奥及布韦语（阿尔冈昆语系）、卡里尔语（Carrier）和德内语（阿萨巴斯卡语系）的字母。</transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="1900">
    <text id="Name">
     <orig>Limbu</orig>
     <transl>林布文字（Limbu）</transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="1950">
    <text id="Name">
     <orig>Tai Le</orig>
     <transl>德宏傣文字（Tai Le）</transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="1980">
    <text id="Name">
     <orig>New Tai Lue</orig>
     <transl>西双版纳新傣文字（New Tai Lue）</transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="19E0">
    <text id="Name">
     <orig>Khmer symbols</orig>
     <transl>高棉文符号（Khmer Symbols）</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="Text">
     <orig>
      <p>The first character of block {{sm|᧠}} is the name of the 8th month in Buddhist solar-lunar calendar (Khmer ''Asat'' or ''Băthámsath'', Sanskrit ''Ashadha'', equivalent to June-July). To prevent lagging behind season changes, this month repeats twice every two or three years. Mark 17D3 {{sm|◌៓}} sometime was [[pt:deprecated|deprecated]] in favour of this character, and in Unicode{{_}}{{vkhmer}} is still not{{_}}recommended.</p>
      <p />
      <p>The rest are the names of days in the lunar calendar from the new moon to full and back.</p>
     </orig>
     <au-cmt>{{vkhmer}} = version that discourages that umlaut</au-cmt>
     <transl>
      <p>该区块的第一个字符 {{sm|᧠}} 是佛教阴阳历中第八个月的名称（高棉语称 ''Asat'' 或 ''Băthámsath''，梵语称 ''Ashadha''，相当于公历的 6 月至 7 月）。为了防止历法与季节变化脱节，这个月份每隔两三年会重复出现两次（即闰月）。符号 17D3 {{sm|◌៓}} 曾一度被 [[pt:deprecated|弃用]] 而改用此字符，且在 Unicode {{vkhmer}} 中目前仍不推荐使用。</p>
      <p />
      <p>其余字符则是阴历中从新月到满月再回到新月的日期名称。</p>
     </transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="1A00">
    <text id="Name">
     <orig>Buginese (Lontara)</orig>
     <transl>布吉文字（Buginese）</transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="1A20">
    <text id="Name">
     <orig>Tai Tham (Lanna)</orig>
     <transl>西双版纳老傣文字（Tai Tham）</transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="1AB0">
    <text id="Name">
     <orig>Combining diacritical marks extended</orig>
     <transl>组合附加记号扩展（Combining Diacritical Marks Extended）</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="Text">
     <orig>Used in German and Scottish dialectology.</orig>
     <transl>用于德语和苏格兰方言学。</transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="1B00">
    <text id="Name">
     <orig>Balinese</orig>
     <transl>巴厘文字（Balinese）</transl>
