    </text>
    <text id="Text">
     <orig>Numbers that were used in Arabic Africa from the 10th to 17th century, especially in Fez ''(Morocco)''.</orig>
     <transl>这是 10 至 17 世纪在阿拉伯非洲地区使用的数字，特别是在摩洛哥的菲斯。</transl>
