    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="10EC0">
    <text id="Text">
     <orig>
      <p>Characters from Turkish and Libyan Quran, and rare variations of Pegon (writing [[ps:Java|Javanese]] with Arabic letters).</p>
      <p />
      <p>“Captial” letters were invented in 1932 by the Egyptian king Fuad{{_}}I.</p>
     </orig>
     <transl>
      <p>来自土耳其和利比亚《古兰经》的字符，以及用阿拉伯字母书写 [[ps:Java|爪哇语]] 的佩贡文（Pegon）的罕见变体。</p>
      <p />
      <p>“大写字母”是由埃及国王福阿德一世于 1932 年发明的。</p>
     </transl>
    </text>
   </group>
