   <group id="11AB0">
    <text id="Name">
     <orig>Canadian Aboriginal syllabics extended A</orig>
     <transl>统一加拿大原住民音节文字扩展 A（Unified Canadian Aboriginal Syllabics Extended-A）</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="Text">
     <orig>Twelve syllables of Inuit (Eskimo) people of Nattilik (literally ''people of seal''), and four historical syllables of Cree and Ojibwe.</orig>
     <transl>纳特西利克因纽特人（字面意思是“海豹人”）的十二个音节，以及克里语和奥吉布瓦语的四个历史音节。</transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="11AC0">
    <text id="Name">
