     <transl>包钦豪文字（Pau Cin Hau）</transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="11B00">
    <text id="Name">
     <orig>Devanagari extended A</orig>
     <transl>天城文字扩展 A（Devanagari Extended-A）</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="Text">
     <orig>Jain punctuation and [[pt:ligature|ligatures]] for phrased like “may it be blessed”.</orig>
     <transl>用于“愿它受祝福”等短语的耆那教标点符号和 [[pt:ligature|连字]]。</transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="11B60">
    <au-cmt>U17</au-cmt>
    <text id="Name">
     <orig>Sharada supplement</orig>
     <transl>夏拉达文字补充（Sharada Supplement）</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="Text">
     <orig>Vowel marks of modern Sharada for Kashmiri, adapted from [[ps:Deva|Devanagari]]. To get initial letters, these marks are attached to [[pu:11183]] or other initial vowel. Kashmiri {{nspk|ks}} is usually written in [[ps:Arab|Arabic-Urdu]].</orig>
     <transl>用于克什米尔语现代夏拉达文的元音标记，改编自 [[ps:Deva|天城文]]。要构成独立的首字母形式，这些标记需要附加在 [[pu:11183]]（即夏拉达文的辅音载体符号）或其他初始元音上。克什米尔语 {{nspk|ks}} 通常使用 [[ps:Arab|阿拉伯-乌尔都文]] 书写。</transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="11BC0">
    <text id="Name">
     <orig>Sunuwar</orig>
     <transl>苏努瓦尔文字（Sunuwar）</transl>
    </text>
   </group>
