   <group id="Text">
    <text id="SmallCap">
     <orig>Small-capital type is used in phonetics, so Unicode has small-capital style for all basic Latin except X.</orig>
     <transl>小型大写字母常用于语音学，因此 Unicode 为除 X 以外的所有基本拉丁字母都设立了小型大写样式。</transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="Misr">
    <text id="Head">
     <orig>{{{{warn|Other images are possible!}} {1}</orig>
     <au-cmt>{1} = placeholder for text, and {{ = escape for {. Right bracket } is not escaped.</au-cmt>
     <transl>{{{{warn|可能存在其他图像！}} {1}</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="U+1F1E6+1F1EB">
     <orig>The current ({{ytalib}}) government, the Taliban, is recognized almost nowhere. Their flag is white with black ''shahada'', the Muslim motto. Meanwhile, vendors use the old flag abandoned in 2021. Sometimes even pre-2013 version, with smaller coat of arms.</orig>
     <au-cmt>{{ytalib}} = year when checked the situation with Taliban, e.g. 2025</au-cmt>
     <transl>现任政府（{{ytalib}}），即塔利班，几乎未得到国际社会的承认。他们的旗帜是白底黑字的“清真言”（伊斯兰教信条）。而在民间，商贩们使用的却是 2021 年被废弃的旧国旗。有时甚至能看到 2013 年以前的版本，也就是国徽较小的那一款。</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="U+1F1E6+1F1F6">
     <orig>As of {{yantarc}}, all vendors use the flag created in 1996 for ''3D World Atlas'' multimedia encyclopedia: UN blue with white continent. A competing flag, navy blue and white with a diamond, has existed since 2018.</orig>
     <au-cmt>{{yantarc}} = year when checked the situation with Antarctica, e.g. 2025 </au-cmt>
     <transl>截至 {{yantarc}}，所有的商贩都在使用一面最初为《3D世界地图集》多媒体百科全书（1996年版）设计的旗帜：那是联合国蓝的底色，上面绘有白色的大陆轮廓。此外，自 2018 年起还出现了一面与之“分庭抗礼”的旗帜，设计为深蓝色底，中间带有白色的菱形图案。</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="U+1F1F2+1F1F6">
     <orig>The red-green-black flag was adopted in 2023. Before that, all vendors used blue French naval ensign with white snakes.</orig>
     <transl>这面红绿黑三色旗是在 2023 年启用的。在此之前，所有的商贩使用的都是带有白色蛇形图案的蓝色法国海军旗。</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="U+1F1ED+1F1F3">
     <orig>In 2022 Honduras made the flag light blue instead of blue.</orig>
     <transl>2022 年，洪都拉斯将国旗的颜色由原本的蓝色改为了浅蓝色。</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="U+1F1EE+1F1F7">
     <orig>In early 2026, Twitter/X reverted to the pre-Islamic flag with a golden lion (1907–1979).</orig>
     <transl>2026 年初，Twitter/X 恢复使用了 1907 年至 1979 年间的伊斯兰化之前旧国旗，那是一面绘有金色狮子的旗帜。</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="U+1F1F8+1F1FE">
     <orig>The Assads’ flag was red-white-black with two stars. The government fled in December 2024, and the flag was changed to green-white-black with three stars (older pre-Assad, but with different aspect ratio).</orig>
     <transl>阿萨德政权的旗帜是红白黑三色，上有两颗星。随着政府在 2024 年 12 月出逃，国旗也随之更换为绿白黑三色并带有三颗星的样式（这虽然是阿萨德时代之前的旧款，但长宽比例有所不同）。</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="U+1F46A">
     <orig>Vendors drew it as man, woman and child until 2019. Later it became genderless. In 2023 it turned to silhouette.</orig>
     <transl>直到 2019 年，供应商还将其描绘为男人、女人和孩子的形象。后来，它变得不再区分性别。到了 2023 年，它又进一步演变成了剪影样式。</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="U+1F4CE">
     <orig>In 2021, Microsoft drew ''Clippit'', the default Microsoft Office assistant. Used in versions 97 to 2003, it was loved for animations and hated for uselessness.</orig>
     <transl>2021 年，微软绘制了“大眼回形针”（Clippit），也就是微软 Office 的默认助手。它曾出现在 97 到 2003 的版本中，大家喜欢它那生动的动画效果，却又因为它总是帮不上忙而讨厌它。</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="U+1F52B">
     <orig>In 2018 the image was changed to a toy to curb threats over the Internet. Despite the consensus, Twitter/X reverted to live gun in 2024.</orig>
     <transl>2018 年，为了遏制网络上的威胁言论，该图像被换成了一把玩具枪。尽管当时大家对此已达成共识，但在 2024 年，Twitter/X 却又将其改回了真枪。</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="U+1F68F">
     <orig>Vendors may draw a variety of local bus stops.</orig>
     <transl>供应商可能会绘制各种各样的本地公交站台。</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="U+1F6DE">
     <orig>Vendors may draw a wheel from horse carriage, bicycle or automobile.</orig>
     <transl>应商可能会绘制马车轮、自行车轮或汽车轮。</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="U+1F9A0">
     <orig>All microscopic creatures are possible: amoeba, bacteria, COVID-19 or other virus.</orig>
     <transl>各种微观生物都有可能出现：比如阿米巴原虫、细菌、新冠病毒或其他病毒。</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="U+1FA85">
     <orig>Google Noto draws star-shaped piñata, and Microsoft does animal-shaped.</orig>
     <transl>Google Noto 绘制的是星形的皮纳塔，而微软则采用了动物造型。</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="U+1FA92">
     <orig>All vendors settled on safety razor relatively recently, in 2019–2021. Windows{{_}}10 emoji depicts a straight razor.</orig>
     <transl>所有供应商在2019-2021年相对较晚地确定了安全剃刀。Windows{{_}}10表情符号描绘的是直剃刀。</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="U+1FAA4">
     <orig>The sample image of Unicode{{_}}{{vtrap}} depicts a spring-loaded trap. But as this emoji mostly means “free cheese” and “entrapment”, most vendors draw a makeshift trap intended to catch the mouse alive, with cheese inside.</orig>
     <transl>Unicode 的示例图片展示的是一种弹簧捕鼠夹。但由于这个表情符号通常寓意着“免费的奶酪”（指天上不会掉馅饼）和“圈套”，大多数厂商选择绘制一种旨在活捉老鼠的简易陷阱，并在里面放上奶酪。</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="Family">
     <orig>Unicode Consortium in early 2023 demanded to draw genderless families as silhouettes (e.g. family film) and move them on “keyboards” from People to Symbols, and recommended to remove gendered ones from “keyboards” and fill with the same silhouettes, to prevent combinatorial explosion. And families often include grandparents and pets. In autumn 2023 Google released their emoji with silhouettes, in spring 2024 Apple did the same. Google’s silhouettes have a little twist: they show women’s haircuts.</orig>
     <transl>2023 年初，Unicode 联盟要求将无性别的家庭形象绘制成剪影（例如家庭电影中的形象），并在“键盘”上将它们从“人物”类别移至“符号”类别。同时，建议移除带有性别区分的家庭表情，并用同样的剪影来填充，以防止组合爆炸。此外，家庭形象也常常包含祖父母和宠物。2023 年秋季，Google 发布了他们的剪影版表情符号，苹果也在 2024 年春季跟进。Google 的剪影还有一个小巧思：它们展示了女性的发型。</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="IO">
     <orig>In 2024, Britain withdrew claims to the uninhabited Chagos Archipelago, giving it to Mauritius but leasing the entire Diego Garcia island, a joint British-US military base. The flag of the British Indian Ocean Territory will likely stay for history, and the flag of Diego Garcia may change.</orig>
     <transl>2024 年，英国放弃了对无人居住的查戈斯群岛的主权要求，将其归还给毛里求斯，但保留了整个迪戈加西亚岛的租赁权，那里是英美联合军事基地。英属印度洋领地的旗帜可能会作为历史文物保留下来，而迪戈加西亚的旗帜则可能会发生变更。</transl>
    </text>
   </group>
