   <group id="Ori">
    <au-cmt>No wiki templates in English origin, but you MAY use them</au-cmt>
    <text id="Brk">
     <orig>{1} ({2})</orig>
     <au-cmt>
      <p>In Western langs — no translation, in Asian — maybe (special brackets or LtR marks)</p>
      <p>1 = reason, always localized</p>
      <p>2 = name, always Latin</p>
     </au-cmt>
     <transl>{1}（{2})）</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="Com">
     <orig>Local/foreign name</orig>
     <au-cmt>Most countries, incl. Turkey</au-cmt>
     <transl>本地 / 外国名称</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="Aut">
     <orig>Local name</orig>
     <au-cmt>e.g. Germany=Deutschland</au-cmt>
     <transl>本地名称</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="Exo">
     <orig>Common foreign name</orig>
     <au-cmt>common=widely used, rather than shared — e.g. Finland=Suomi, Russia=Rossiya, Montenegro=Crna Gora</au-cmt>
     <transl>通用外国名称</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="Old">
     <orig>Old name</orig>
     <au-cmt>e.g. for Eswatini=Swaziland, Cambodia=Khmer</au-cmt>
     <transl>旧称</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="Fre">
     <orig>Free code</orig>
     <au-cmt>for some new/renamed countries like Benin, Guernsey, Serbia when it’s hard even to find a suitable code</au-cmt>
     <transl>自由分配代码</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="Eur">
     <orig>European name for land</orig>
     <au-cmt>some scarcely inhabited islands</au-cmt>
     <transl>欧洲对这片土地的称呼</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="Tur">
     <orig>Foreign name of Russian origin + old Romanization of local Cyrillic</orig>
     <au-cmt>for Kazakhstan=Qazaqstan, Uzbekistan=Ozbekiston</au-cmt>
     <transl>源自俄语的外国名称 + 当地西里尔字母的旧式罗马化拼写</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="en">
     <orig>English</orig>
     <au-cmt>for Hungary=Magyar and some islands</au-cmt>
     <transl>英国</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="es">
     <orig>Spanish</orig>
     <au-cmt>for some colonies related to Spain, e.g. West Sahara</au-cmt>
     <transl>西班牙</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="fr">
     <orig>French</orig>
     <au-cmt>For Antarctica=Antarctique and more</au-cmt>
     <transl>法国</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="la">
     <orig>Latin</orig>
     <au-cmt>For Switzerland=Confoederatio Helvetica</au-cmt>
     <transl>拉丁</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="nl">
     <orig>Dutch</orig>
     <au-cmt>For South Africa=Zuid Afrika</au-cmt>
     <transl>荷兰</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="ru">
     <orig>Russian</orig>
     <au-cmt>For Belarus=Byelorussia</au-cmt>
     <transl>俄罗斯</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="BQ">
     <orig>Free code; another name is Bonaire, Saba, and Sint Eustatius</orig>
     <au-cmt>For Caribbean Netherlands</au-cmt>
     <transl>自由分配代码；另一个名称是博奈尔、萨巴和圣尤斯特歇斯</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="CQ">
     <orig>Free code; Norman French</orig>
     <au-cmt>For Sark=Sercq</au-cmt>
     <transl>自由分配代码；诺曼法国</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="SX">
     <orig>Free code; code for Princess Juliana Airport</orig>
     <au-cmt>for Dutch St Martin</au-cmt>
     <transl>自由分配代码；朱莉安娜公主机场</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="TW">
     <orig>The official name “Republic of China” is almost never used by foreigners</orig>
     <au-cmt>For Taiwan</au-cmt>
     <transl>外国人几乎从不使用“中华民国”这个官方名称。</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="UA">
     <orig>UK is reserved for Great Britain</orig>
     <au-cmt>For Ukraine</au-cmt>
     <transl>UK 专用于大不列颠</transl>
    </text>
    <text id="XK">
     <orig>Temporary EU code</orig>
     <au-cmt>For Kosovo</au-cmt>
     <transl>欧盟临时代码</transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <text id="Favs">
    <orig>Favourites work with single characters only</orig>
    <au-cmt>
     <p>Test:</p>
     <p>1. Lib, complex emoji like Animals→Birds→phoenix</p>
     <p>2. Click heart button that’s greyed</p>
    </au-cmt>
    <transl>收藏夹仅支持单个字符</transl>
   </text>
