   <group id="1.1">
    <text id="Text">
     <orig>
      <p>The first version that became an ISO standard, and the first existing in Unicode bases. The bases of 1.0 and 1.0.1 are reconstructed.</p>
      <p />
      <p>Version 1.0 (October 1991, ≈{{n|7200}} characters) added most scripts of 1.1, including [[ps:Tibt|Tibetan]] deleted in 1.1, and {{n|2350}} [[ps:Hang|Hangul]] syllables that would be deleted in [[pv:2.0|2.0]].</p>
      <p />
      <p>Version 1.0.1 (June 1992, ≈{{n|28300}} characters) added {{n|20902}} [[ps:Hani|CJK ideographs]], and deleted 6 characters.</p>
      <p />
      <p>Version 1.1 added {{n|4306}} more Hangul characters, and deleted Tibetan.</p>
     </orig>
     <transl>
      <p>这是首个成为 ISO 标准的版本，也是现存 Unicode 的基础版本。1.0 和 1.0.1 版本的基础数据是经过重构的。</p>
      <p />
      <p>版本 1.0（1991 年 10 月，约 {{n|7200}} 个字符）：增加了大部分后来属于 1.1 版本的文字脚本，包括在 1.1 版本中被删除的 [[ps:Tibt|藏文]]，以及 {{n|2350}} 个在 [[pv:2.0|2.0]] 版本中被删除的 [[ps:Hang|韩文音节]]。</p>
      <p />
      <p>版本 1.0.1（1992 年 6 月，约 {{n|28300}} 个字符）：增加了 {{n|20902}} 个 [[ps:Hani|中日韩统一表意文字]]，并删除了 6 个字符。</p>
      <p />
      <p>版本 1.1：增加了 {{n|4306}} 个额外的韩文字符，并删除了藏文。</p>
     </transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="2.0">
    <text id="Text">
     <orig>Version 2.0 moved [[pt:precomposed|precomposed]] [[ps:Hang|Hangul]] syllables to their current place. After a great outcry, Unicode adopted the main [[pt:stability|stability]] guarantee: the character will not move or disappear.</orig>
     <transl>2.0 版本将 [[pt:precomposed|预组合]] 的 [[ps:Hang|韩文]] 音节移动到了它们现在的位置。在一片强烈的抗议声之后，Unicode 采纳了主要的 [[pt:stability|稳定性]] 保证：字符将不再移动或消失。</transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="2.1">
    <text id="Text">
     <orig>Added euro '''[[pc:20AC|€]]''' and object replacement character [[pc:FFFC]].</orig>
     <transl>新增了欧元符号 '''[[pc:20AC|€]]''' 和对象替换符 [[pc:FFFC]]。</transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="3.1">
    <text id="Text">
     <orig>The first use of [[pt:plane|planes]] 1 and 2. [[pt:utf16|UTF-16]] and sixteen supplementary planes were proposed five years before.</orig>
     <transl>这是 [[pt:plane|平面]] 1 和 2 的首次使用。而 [[pt:utf16|UTF-16]] 编码标准以及 16 个辅助平面的构想，其实在五年前就已经被提出了。</transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="4.1">
    <text id="Text">
     <orig>{{GrekCoptUni}}</orig>
     <au-cmt>You see, snippet only and no need to translate</au-cmt>
     <transl>{{GrekCoptUni}}</transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="6.2">
    <text id="Text">
     <orig>Added Turkish lira sign [[pc:20BA]] presented in March 2012.</orig>
     <transl>新增了 2012 年 3 月发布的土耳其里拉符号 [[pc:20BA]]。</transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="6.3">
    <text id="Text">
     <orig>Five [[pt:format|format]] characters for [[pt:bidi|bidirectional]] text.</orig>
     <transl>新增了 5 个用于 [[pt:bidi|双向]] 文本的 [[pt:format|格式]] 字符。</transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="12.1">
    <text id="Text">
     <orig>Emergency release of Unicode containing one character [[pc:32FF]], the Reiwa era of Japanese traditional calendar. In 2016, the old Emperor Akihito decided to abdicate, and a new code point was reserved for his heir. When he finally abdicated on 30 April 2019, the character was quickly encoded.</orig>
     <transl>这是一次 Unicode 紧急发布，仅包含一个字符 [[pc:32FF]]，即日本传统历法中的“令和”年号。早在 2016 年，明仁天皇决定退位时，就已经为他的继承人预留了一个新的码点。当他最终于 2019 年 4 月 30 日退位后，该字符迅速被编码。</transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="15.1">
    <text id="Text">
     <orig>
      <p>Unicode Consortium experienced staff problems: the release manager had gone, and the Sinologist died. So they decided to make a minor release: five ideographic description characters, 18 right-facing emoji, and 10 emoji sequences including lime, phoenix, and silhouettes of families.</p>
      <p />
      <p>The Chinese government also forced to do an urgent job, see [[pk:2EBF0|CJK ideographs extension I]].</p>
      <p />
      <p>A very big release 16.0 is expected in 2024.</p>
     </orig>
     <transl>
      <p>Unicode 联盟遭遇了人员问题：发布经理离职，汉学家去世。因此，他们决定进行一次小版本更新：包含 5 个表意文字描述字符、18 个向右看的表情符号，以及 10 个表情符号序列（包括青柠、凤凰和家庭剪影）。</p>
      <p />
      <p>与此同时，中国政府也在紧急处理相关工作，参见 [[pk:2EBF0|中日韩统一表意文字扩展 I 区]]。</p>
     </transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="16.0">
    <text id="Text">
     <orig>
      <p>Besides character additions, there were many internal changes in Unicode.</p>
      <p>* Rewrote algorithms for rendering Arabic text.</p>
      <p>* Wrote character sequences that should not exist in Unicode text.</p>
      <p>* Added base of Egyptian hieroglyphs.</p>
      <p>* Turned the PDF specification into an HTML site.</p>
      <p />
      <p>Unicode{{_}}16 might have exactly {{n|155000}} characters (excluding 65 [[pt:control|control]]){{-}}but two Indic [[pt:ligature|ligatures]] were removed.</p>
     </orig>
     <transl>
      <p>除了增加字符外，Unicode 内部还发生了许多变化：</p>
      <p>* 重写了阿拉伯文本的渲染算法。</p>
      <p>* 编写（定义）了在 Unicode 文本中不应存在的字符序列。</p>
      <p>* 增加了埃及象形文字的基础。</p>
      <p>* 将 PDF 格式的规范文档转为 HTML 网站。</p>
      <p />
      <p>Unicode{{_}}16 可能正好包含 {{n|155000}} 个字符（不包括 65 个 [[pt:control|控制字符]]）——但有两个印度文字 [[pt:ligature|连字]] 被移除了。</p>
     </transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="17.0">
    <text id="Text">
     <orig>
      <p>* Written [[pt:egyp|rules]] of encoding Egyptian hieroglyphs, swapped glyphs [[pc:130F9]]↔[[pc:13ABE|ABE]] and [[pc:130FB]]↔[[pc:13AE8|AE8]] for compatibility with Gardiner’s list</p>
      <p>* Reformed [[ps:Adlm|Adlam]] script for better legibility</p>
      <p>* Added a [[pt:inclusion|genderless]] version of the last emoji{{-}}dancer: Latin for a woman, disco for a man, and ballet for genderless</p>
      <p>* Added the last multiracial emoji{{-}}wrestlers and Playboy girls</p>
      <p>* In early 2025, the sign for Saudi riyal was adopted and quickly put to [[pu:20C1]]</p>
     </orig>
     <transl>
      <p>* 制定了 [[pt:egyp|编码]] 埃及象形文字的规则，并交换了 [[pc:130F9]] ↔ [[pc:13ABE|ABE]] 和 [[pc:130FB]] ↔ [[pc:13AE8|AE8]] 的字形，以兼容加德纳（Gardiner）列表。</p>
      <p>* 改革了 [[ps:Adlm|阿德拉姆文字]]（Adlam），以提高其可读性。</p>
      <p>* 为最后一个表情符号——舞者——添加了 [[pt:inclusion|无性别]] 版本：拉丁舞代表女性，迪斯科代表男性，芭蕾舞代表无性别。</p>
      <p>* 添加了最后一个多种族表情符号——摔跤手和花花公子女孩。</p>
      <p>* 2025 年初，沙特里亚尔的符号被采纳，并迅速被分配到了 [[pu:20C1]]。</p>
     </transl>
    </text>
   </group>
   <group id="18.0">
    <text id="Text">
     <orig>
      <p>* Steady improvements in [[pt:egyp|Egyptian]] for compatibility with Gardiner’s list. In particular, swapped [[pc:13277]]↔[[pc:13FDC]].</p>
      <p>* Multiple musical symbols, including long-awaited [[pc:1D1EB|half-sharp]] and [[pc:1D1ED|half-flat]] from modern software.</p>
      <p>* Historical [[ps:Latn|Latin]]-based transcription.</p>
      <p>* Old mathematical notations.</p>
      <p>* [[pk:10EC0|Arabic]] “capital” letters (Egypt, 1932).</p>
     </orig>
     <transl>
      <p>*  [[pt:egyp|埃及文字]] 持续改进以兼容加德纳列表。特别是交换了 [[pc:13277]] ↔ [[pc:13FDC]]。</p>
      <p>* 新增了多个音乐符号，包括现代软件中期待已久的 [[pc:1D1EB|升半音号]] 和 [[pc:1D1ED|降半音号]]。</p>
      <p>* 收录了基于 [[ps:Latn|拉丁文字]] 的历史转写字符。</p>
      <p>* 收录了古老的数学符号。</p>
      <p>* 收录了 [[pk:10EC0|阿拉伯文字]] “大写”字母（埃及，1932 年）。</p>
     </transl>
    </text>
   </group>
  </group>
  <group id="Update">
   <text id="Head">
    <orig>Check for update</orig>
    <au-cmt>Dialog header</au-cmt>
    <transl>检查更新</transl>
   </text>
   <text id="Ok">
    <orig>You are using the latest version {1}.</orig>
    <transl>您正在使用最新版本 {1}。</transl>
   </text>
   <text id="Earlier">
    <orig>Strange: my version is {1}, the repository has {2}. Probably the repository has migrated, or you have a non-public development version.</orig>
    <au-cmt>Test: in Unicodia.xml add parameter debug-update/version=[smth big like "10.1.2"]</au-cmt>
    <transl>异常：当前版本是 {1}，但存储库中有 {2}。可能是存储库已迁移，或者您使用的是非公开的开发版本。</transl>
   </text>
   <text id="Later">
    <orig>My version is {1}, found update to {2}. Go to repository?</orig>
    <au-cmt>Test: in Unicodia.xml add parameter debug-update/version=[smth small like "1.2.3"]</au-cmt>
    <transl>当前版本是 {1}，发现可更新到 {2}。要转到存储库吗？</transl>
   </text>
   <text id="BadVer">
    <orig>Strange: cannot parse version “{1}”.</orig>
    <au-cmt>Test: in Unicodia.xml add parameter debug-update/version="0.0.2" (exactly)</au-cmt>
    <transl>异常：无法解析版本“{1}”。</transl>
   </text>
   <text id="Connect">
    <orig>Cannot connect to repository. Check your internet connection.</orig>
    <au-cmt>Test: pull off internet cable, or disconnect from WiFi</au-cmt>
    <transl>无法连接到存储库。请检查您的互联网连接。</transl>
   </text>
   <text id="Err">
    <orig>Strange: got error code {1}. Something happened to repository.</orig>
    <au-cmt>Test: in Unicodia.xml add parameter debug-update/version="0.0.3" (exactly)</au-cmt>
    <transl>异常：收到错误代码{1}。存储库可能出现问题。</transl>
   </text>
   <text id="Go">
    <orig>&amp;Go</orig>
    <au-cmt>Test: same as Later</au-cmt>
    <transl>前往 (&amp;G)</transl>
   </text>
   <text id="Close">
    <orig>&amp;Close</orig>
    <au-cmt>Test: same as Later</au-cmt>
    <transl>关闭 (&amp;C)</transl>
   </text>
   <text id="Parse">
    <orig>Strange: cannot parse server’s reply.</orig>
    <au-cmt>Test: in Unicodia.xml add parameter debug-update/version="0.0.1" (exactly)</au-cmt>
    <transl>异常：无法解析服务器的回复。</transl>
   </text>
   <text id="Abandon">
    <orig>Your platform “{1}” seems to be abandoned. You’ll have to go to home page for yourself and find a suitable platform.</orig>
    <au-cmt>Test: in Unicodia.xml add parameter debug-update/version=[smth small like "1.0"], platforms=[smth odd like "xxx"]</au-cmt>
    <transl>您的平台“{1}”似乎已被放弃。您将需要转到主页并为自己找到一个合适的平台。</transl>
   </text>
  </group>
